content:
On Saturday in the afternoon, the Russians launched a ballistic missile in the Odessa region, probably Iskander-M.

About thisreportedDefense forces of South of Ukraine.

The launch occurred from the temporarily occupied Crimea, the rocket hit the open territory of the Belgorod-Dnestrovsky district.

Information on destruction and victims did not receive.

It is also reported that the enemy continues active unmanned reconnaissance from the sea. The defense of the South of Ukraine over the Black Sea destroyed two Zala reconnaissance drones.

“Be conscious and attentive, promptly respond to warnings about the danger, go to the shelter. Do not interfere with the work forces of defense and do not help the enemy information about the work of the air defense, ”the message said.
